8 An Act relating to sunsets; repealing 63 O.S. 2021,
Section 1-1923, as amended by Section 1, Chapter 197,
9 O.S.L. 2023 (63 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 1-1923),
which relates to the Long-Term Care Facility Advisory
10 Board; providing an effective date; and declaring an
emergency.
11
12
13
14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. REPEALER 63 O.S. 2021, Section 1-1923, as
16 amended by Section 1, Chapter 197, O.S.L. 2023 (63 O.S. Supp. 2025,
17 Section 1-1923), is hereby repealed.
18 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective July 1, 2026.
19 SECTION 3. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
20 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
21 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
22 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
